name: Digital Revolution and Transcendence
description: After Identity Crisis and Existential Crisis, we are destined to deal with a digital crisis and seek digital freedom from all the medias to which we are connected and in which we are emprisoned. Digital detox and isolation or deprivation tanks will relieve us temporarily but not endlessly. For more you can pre-order my illustrated book:  HTTP://ikigai.alahay.org. Keywords, Digital revolution, ai, digital feminism, transcendence, transhumanism, digital age, digital freedom
